{"repo": {"timestamp": 1774734857375, "version": 30000, "name": "Keyguard Project", "icon": "icon.png", "address": "https://gh.artemchep.com/keyguard-repo-fdroid/repo", "description": "Mirrors artifacts available on https://github.com/AChep/keyguard-app/releases"}, "requests": {"install": [], "uninstall": []}, "apps": [{"authorEmail": "mail@artemchep.com", "authorName": "Artem Chepurnyi", "categories": ["keyguard-repo-fdroid"], "suggestedVersionCode": "2147483647", "description": "<p><i>Can be used with any Bitwarden\u00ae installation. This product is not associated with the Bitwarden project nor Bitwarden, Inc. Bitwarden\u00ae is a registered trademark of Bitwarden Inc.</i></p>\n<p><b>Highlights</b></p>\n- a beautiful rich and responsive <b>Material You</b> user interface;\n- a <b>powerful</b> and <b>fast search</b>;\n- a support for creating & using <b>passkeys</b> - a modern alternative to passwords.\n- a watchtower that finds items with <b>Pwned passwords</b>, <b>Vulnerable accounts</b>, <b>Reused passwords</b>, <b>Inactive two factor authentication</b>, <b>Inactive passkeys</b>, <b>Unsecure Websites</b> as well as <b>Duplicate</b>, <b>Incomplete</b> and <b>Expiring</b> items, and other;\n- <b>multi-account support</b> with secure login and two-factor authentication support;\n- add items and sends, modify, and view your vault offline.\n- beautiful <b>Light/Dark theme</b>;\n- a generator with <b>Email forwarders</b>, <b>Custom wordlists</b> support and many other features;\n- a support for <b>placeholders</b> and <b>URL overrides</b>;\n- and much more!", "issueTracker": "https://github.com/AChep/keyguard-app/issues", "license": "Unknown", "name": "Keyguard", "sourceCode": "https://github.com/AChep/keyguard-app", "summary": "An alternative client for the Bitwarden\u00ae platform", "translation": "https://crowdin.com/project/keyguard", "added": 1772292281000, "packageName": "com.artemchep.keyguard", "lastUpdated": 1774734853903, "localized": {"en-US": {"featureGra